<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/27867133">在LES中计算Dynamic Smagorinsky Model Coefficient时对方程右侧取的是什么平均？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3329684" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">在大涡模拟(LES)中Germano Dynamic Model的<a class=" wrap external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Large_eddy_simulation#Germano_dynamic_model" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">相关wiki页面<i class="icon-external"></i></a>中, 我注意它在计算Smagorinsky Coefficient (Cs)时对方程右侧的取了一个平均以提高数值稳定性，这个平均是何种意义上的呢（时间，空间 or 系综）?<br><img data-rawheight="172" data-rawwidth="616" src="//pic4.zhimg.com/9524bf2ba057e4672004d104b006ee63_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/9524bf2ba057e4672004d104b006ee63_r.jpg"></div>


</div>
