<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730"
class="zm-item-link-avatar"
href="/people/kaiserwang730">
<img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg"
class="zm-list-avatar"
data-source="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="49">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$li-jing-jie-98" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/li-jing-jie-98" class="zg-link" title="李竞捷">李竞捷</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ge-lan-fen-duo-jia-shi-fen" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ge-lan-fen-duo-jia-shi-fen" class="zg-link" title="格兰芬多加十分">格兰芬多加十分</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$jiao-chao-ran" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/jiao-chao-ran" class="zg-link" title="焦超然">焦超然</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3329684" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">谢邀。<br><br>Lilly, D. K. (1992). "A proposed modification of the Germano subgrid-scale closure method". <i>Physics of Fluids A</i> 4 (3): 633–636：<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/fca8c3ea8c849749e2d5093fd4262f7f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="515" data-rawheight="59" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="515" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/fca8c3ea8c849749e2d5093fd4262f7f_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="515" data-rawheight="59" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="515" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/fca8c3ea8c849749e2d5093fd4262f7f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/fca8c3ea8c849749e2d5093fd4262f7f_b.jpg"><br>这里的C就是题图里的Cs²<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/d39f103a1979a91c9d680caae6838493_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="515" data-rawheight="327" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="515" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/d39f103a1979a91c9d680caae6838493_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="515" data-rawheight="327" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="515" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/d39f103a1979a91c9d680caae6838493_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/d39f103a1979a91c9d680caae6838493_b.jpg"><br>“Moin[7]说呢，公式(11)已经测出挺好的结果了。他指出，但是呢，那个吧，在单个网格节点上，C的值有时还是挺大，计算不稳定了。 我们对(11)做了一个简单的统计分析（怎么分析的不告诉你），假定Lij和Mij但服从高斯分布。 然后就发现啊，C的方差和(σL/σM)²成正比，这个σL和σM<br>分别是L和M的标准差。比例系数与自由度负相关，说明平均可以避免过大值。 或者呢，孤立的特别大的C可以直接抹掉。”<br><br>所以呢，这个平均是统计平均。<br><br><br>我本来想看看Moin在引用[7]原话是咋说的，结果发现参考文献里是这么写的：<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/47ba1146aae3246f50001f7fa93e8306_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="265" data-rawheight="32" class="content_image" width="265"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="265" data-rawheight="32" class="content_image lazy" width="265" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/47ba1146aae3246f50001f7fa93e8306_b.jpg"><br>我仿佛听到：<br><br>“那个美国的Parviz Moin，比你们不知高到哪里去了，我跟他privately communicate.”


</div>

</div>
